snippet.title: ALAN-13 Reformation trailer
snippet.description:
Our first trailer is out! A fun logical puzzle game, which makes you think like a programmer. 

Check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1888130/ALAN13_Reformation

You can find more about us at: https://www.smithandcherryapps.com/alan13
